room_title: Escape room "Shipwrecked" by Challenges East Lansing in Lansing
room_address: 3044 E Lake Lansing Rd, East Lansing, MI 48823
room_description:
Find your way around Captain Salazar's cabin and find his most prized and valuable possessions before strange things start happening on the haunted ship. You have 60 minutes before Captain Salazar arrives and haunts you forever.
While there is nothing scary about this room, it does take place in low light.
